Rating: 4
This recipe was so good, that for the first time ever I've decided to write a review. I did have to make some changes for what I had on hand...yellow miso instead of red, cod instead of bass, a mix of shiitake and cremini mushrooms...it turned out beautifully. I also sauteed some cut up bok choy in a pan and added that to the soup so it was more substantial. My husband said it was by far my most successful culinary experiment ever and we can't wait to try it again...maybe with scallops next time? I think the flavors will go. DEEELISH. And so easy to make!

